title: 'Product exudes quality and ruggedness'
body: The product quality exceeded my expectations. I was expecting run-of-the-mill material and fit-and-finish. I am pleasantly surprised on both counts. The buckle and belt are very well-finished. They are nicely weighted and feel solid.  I hope that the buckle polish stays intact over the long run without chips, nicks and scratches and that the belt material also maintains its shape, stitching and overall finish. As of now, I don't see any reason why this cannot be the case.
